Notes: Minnesota Duluth ranked #25 in NCAA Division II.
MSU's Kelli Freeman scored 1000th career point in second half, becoming 11th
Maverick in school history to join the 1000 Point Club.
Freeman also became MSU's all-time 3-Point FG Leader in 2nd half.
